<problem id="fs-idm250828432">
<para id="fs-idm235632000">Whitman frequently uses the verb “sing” throughout <emphasis effect="italics">Leaves of Grass</emphasis>. What do you suppose is the meaning of this word, according to Whitman? In what ways do Whitman and the people he depicts “sing” throughout the anthology?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm525767568">
<problem id="fs-idm230794992">
<para id="fs-idm260519072">Evaluate the extent to which Whitman’s poetry addresses issues that were of importance to transcendentalists in the nineteenth century.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
